======================================================
 Time Schedule
======================================================
 Time precision patch is 1e-05

=====|    Phase I     |===============================
-----. CPM .------------------------------------
  + 0.3 => CPM [R,Rho,prot] -> [cell.center,cell.length,cell.surface,cell.type,cell.volume]
-----. Reactions .------------------------------------
  + 0.01 => System [WavePinning Rac] [H,Rho,delta,gamma,k_0,k_1,n,s,s_1] -> [H,P2,P3,R,R_i]
  + 0.01 => System [WavePinning Rho] [H,K_T,R,T_0,Tension,delta_rho,gamma_rho,k_0_rho,k_1_rho,n,n_T,s_1_rho] -> [Rho,Rho_i]
  + 0.01 => System [cell.surface,cell.volume,targ_Perimeter] -> [Area,Perimeter,Tension]

=====|    Phase II    |===============================
-----. Reporters and Instantaneous Processes.---------
  + -1 => Mapper [Polarity extraction from membrane] [R,cell.center] -> [p]
  + 0.3 => Protrusion [prot] -> [prot]
  + 0.3 => Mapper [Sensing the field] [U,cell.center] -> [s]

=====|    Phase III   |===============================
-----. Analysis .-------------------------------------
  + 1 => CellTracker [cell.center] 
  + 6000 => ModelGraph [] 
  + 5 => Logger [R,R_i,Rho,Rho_i,Tension,m.phi,s] 
  + 10 => Gnuplotter [U,cell.type] 
------------------------------------------------------
